      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home! This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it garage-kept and totally spotless. It drives like an absolute dream! If you\u2019re looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it. Drop me a message and come see it for yourself\u2014you're going to love it!",
